Corning’s Glass Solution to a Plastic Problem
Corning’s Glass Solution to a Plastic Problem

												Corning Lotus™ NXT Glass plays a vital role in OLED handheld devices, even if the display panel uses a plastic backplane. How is that possible?

												Corning Lotus™ NXT Glass plays a vital role in OLED handheld devices, even if the display panel uses a plastic backplane. How is that possible?

