The Extrusion Process


The Extrusion Process

												Our extrusion process is used to create ceramic substrates and particulate filters, which help reduce harmful vehicle emissions.

												Our extrusion process is used to create ceramic substrates and particulate filters, which help reduce harmful vehicle emissions.

												Learn More 














 









Vapor Deposition Process



Vapor Deposition Process

												The vapor depostion process is used to create preforms
 that are then drawn to create optical fiber.

												The vapor depostion process is used to create preforms
 that are then drawn to create optical fiber.

												Learn More 













The Fusion Process
The Fusion Process

												The fusion process, one of our key manufacturing and engineering platforms, creates high-quality flat 
glass used in today's consumer electronics.

												The fusion process, one of our key manufacturing and engineering platforms, creates high-quality flat 
glass used in today's consumer electronics.

												Learn More 
















